{"tid":512610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警涉藏毒　受審前暈倒入院","createTime":"2017-12-28T16:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T02:44:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0da9b12a158509b9442d2abaea70daa9d6837336","tid":512610,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171228/20257232?_ga=2.146532468.1341776848.1514259600-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171228%2F20257232%3F_ga%3D2.146532468.1341776848.1514259600-581282530.1504247435&d=kMmdTZ32BPJnEET%2FCq9WyRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6de210a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171228%2F20257232%3F_ga%3D2.146532468.1341776848.1514259600-581282530.1504247435&h=770e45d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171228/20257232?_ga=2.146532468.1341776848.1514259600-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n警涉藏毒　受審前暈倒入院<br />\n<br />\n5,948<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171228/large/28ls3p21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171228%2Flarge%2F28ls3p21.jpg&h=885b49b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】一名高級警員於休班期間涉藏有俗稱K仔的毒品氯胺酮，在街頭遭同袍截查被捕，案件原定昨天在西九龍法院開審，但辯方指潘凌晨時分暈倒被送入屯門醫院，獲醫生簽發一天病假，不能到庭，裁判官遂將案件押後至明年3月14日才開審。由於控方證人涉及警方刑事情報科人員，因此證人屆時獲准在屏風後作供，免身份被公開。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告潘俊東（40歲，圖）於去年10月28日在荃灣綠楊新邨D座旁的行人路管有藏於膠袋內的0.38克K仔。據知警方毒品調查科接獲線報後暗中派人進行跟蹤行動時，發現有人涉進行毒品交易而揭發本案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC4947/17<br />\n■記者黃幗慧  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n洩92客資料　星展經理判社服"},{"pid":"78953bbb3edd614a84ab008be978170a7318ca33","tid":512610,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"喳架"}]}